{"tid":1889130,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】48歲初步確診軍裝警駐守北角 妻子外母現病徵","createTime":"2020-02-20T14:01:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T17:11:58.000Z","uid":29627,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"69fdefebda65eabf8356f1dd3a10aeab15d005aa","tid":1889130,"uid":29627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T14:01:42.000Z","msg":"【武漢肺炎】48歲初步確診軍裝警駐守北角 妻子外母現病徵<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200220/large/1582206877_32e0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200220%2Flarge%2F1582206877_32e0.jpg&h=f847a8c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本港晚上再新增一宗初步確診個案，患者為一名48歲軍裝警員。據悉，該名警員前日（18日）發燒，他近日到觀塘普通科門診求診後，再自行留唾液送交測試，樣本測試初步呈陽性反應。聯合醫院通知他後，由救護車將他送聯合醫院隔離治療。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，患者居於油美苑潤美閣紀律部隊宿舍，駐守北角警署軍裝巡邏第4小隊。他2月18日出席了一個60人的退休宴會，地點在西環明星酒家，同日就發燒。有公院醫護透露，該名警員在觀塘普通科門診留唾液檢測初步呈陽性，其妻子及外母亦有病徵，已將樣本一拼送醫院再檢驗。而西環明星酒家於昨日起突然停業，屬同一集團的北角明星酒家於日前亦突然停業，該處早前為康美樓感染群組聚餐地點。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，當日出席宴會的人士大部份駐守西區警署，警方正追蹤有關人士。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局由本月19日起擴大新型冠狀病毒檢測範圍，為症狀輕微的急症室及普通科門診病人進行檢測，由病人自行留唾液再交回急症室或門診進行測試。今次是首次門診化驗而確診個案。<br />\n<br />\n軍裝警員初步確診時序<br />\n<br />\n2月18日 到西環明星酒家出席60人聚會<br />\n2月19日 請病假到觀塘普通科門診求診<br />\n2月20日 請病假，將自行留唾液送交測試<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200220/VWV6SVH5E55HVC3XMQFSY6V6KQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200220%2FVWV6SVH5E55HVC3XMQFSY6V6KQ&d=1mfmSgVVN%2FWy7xf%2FaESqF3lPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=c63cab98\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200220%2FVWV6SVH5E55HVC3XMQFSY6V6KQ&h=ad757832\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200220/VWV6SVH5E55HVC3XMQFSY6V6KQ</a>"},{"pid":"b4d030ed1102d867b4e40ac9a17ae3bd0dc0f7fe","tid":1889130,"uid":126621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T14:03:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qb8eE5K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqb8eE5K.jpg&h=171564bc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5da432c7aba44002b8dcdf2ca38f83223b3d38bb","tid":1889130,"uid":37528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T14:04:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好俾佢停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85785ba14b0ec307bf72c1220c64acc3b113cdb6","tid":1889130,"uid":37528,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T14:04:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VjmTbpr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVjmTbpr.jpg&h=0b85cabe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n集氣呀"},{"pid":"3026f72b80090f17ba19407d0ae2c6bf8bd5c3f8","tid":1889130,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T14:50:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4QZJyS7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4QZJyS7.gif&h=762a6a48&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"13eb7abda079925653c47069c271d8bf78c631c8","tid":1889130,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T16